{"tid":573218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭耀棠：修憲是人民意志　反問「阻住地球轉是否要革新？」","createTime":"2018-02-26T09:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T15:53:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"97c3c34665ab3029313ab3934c95fd5056203ecc","tid":573218,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180226/s00001/2d2aed79b1912110c7ce3b32516c14ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180226%2Fs00001%2F2d2aed79b1912110c7ce3b32516c14ea.jpg&h=ca1a2a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共中央建議修憲，包括刪除國家主席「連續任職不得超過兩屆」的任期限制。工聯會港區全國人大代表鄭耀棠認為，修憲是「人民的意志」，不存在倒退或前進，「當人民有強烈的要求，有強烈的民意基礎，邊個人，邊個黨，都無法抗拒」。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會召開記者會講解兩會提案建議。被問到對修憲立場，鄭耀棠說，目前尚未收到文本，要稍後看過相關文件後再決定立場。但鄭表示，修憲是「人民的意志」。<br />\n<br />\n對於已故國家領導人鄧小平曾經說：「把一個國家、一個黨的穩定建立在一兩個人的威望上，是靠不住的。」鄭耀棠回應指：「鄧小平退下來的時候，都是無職位，但當時的環境，誰說了算？」鄭續說：「任何人的言論都有一個經歷，馬克思過去的說話，是否完全啱用於現在？」<br />\n<br />\n問到鄧小平那套對，還是中共中央今次建議的對，鄭耀棠稱：「這個無對與錯。我今日做的事我認為對的事，但過了一段時間，已經我落後了，我做的事已不適合整個社會發展，或者我這個做法阻住個地球轉架喇，這樣是否要進行革新啊？要進行革命啊？」<br />\n<br />\n另外，工聯會將在兩會期間，提岀多項涉及「粤港澳大灣區」發展建議，希望可以提高港人在內地岀行保障和生活便利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180226/s00001/1519633027359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180226%2Fs00001%2F1519633027359&d=5L0f0P31qWqUGS%2FEmTu3LKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=1636bd1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180226%2Fs00001%2F1519633027359&h=70eafb7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180226/s00001/1519633027359</a>"},{"pid":"791959ec350aae8f0556fad2311bb39978a8bb57","tid":573218,"uid":40628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"買定離手喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b199ffbf65071e61869ab33d743cc7e56dff3182","tid":573218,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"做一世主席就真係阻住地球轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53471b9d3647fa381e35e9074eda7675aafbb67e","tid":573218,"uid":53687,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"鄭耀棠想革命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039a3705c770d392838d4cfde895228a74779374","tid":573218,"uid":35430,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"人呢意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢連自己都呃埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710bdf2502e049b93c6920e5699f93d99b3574fc","tid":573218,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人民意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢連自己都呃埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5bf98c623aa7c5a5ef73e4906b733b7cd073e7b1","tid":573218,"uid":44358,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"